Body: Description: The SQL Solution Set reports contain stale data from SQL Servers that have either been decommissioned or moved to AWS RDS instances.  I would like to remove all of the SQL tables that contain all of this stale data and start fresh with only the SQL Servers that are active.

Doesn't look like there is an instant job for this like some of the other DCs have. Opened a SWAT thread:

Tay Caliguiri: Drop SQL Host data

posted in SWAT Teams: Product Discussions, PM Q&A, Feedback / NEA for Databases on Monday, December 2, 2024 1:55 PM
